to be called. .I would recommend Hotel 1898 as a great place to stay, especially for the wonderful rooftop terrace and the central location but don鈥檛 ask the staff for tips or advice and make sure they don鈥檛 put you into one of the small and dark corner rooms on the inner courtyard. Oh, and watch out for the 2 elderly gentlemen standing by reception 鈥?I have no idea what their role was as they never spoke, never assisted with anything, never did anything in fact, but they were always there- management perhaps, but what they were managing I do not know? 
